description: All of Baltimore is raving about the scrumptious spuds from Craving Potato Factory. Every baked potato they make is loaded to absolute perfection. Their selection includes these faves: Craving Classic & Simple (gourmet baked potato with broccoli, four cheeses, sour cream, and chives), Ravenstown Steak (with marinated steak, cheddar cheese, truffle oil, onions, pepper, chives) and of course, the oh-so-delicious Orioles Old Bay Lump Crab, just to name a few. For a gourmet baked potato that is sure to make your day, you may just have to visit the Craving Potato Factory.
name: Craving Potato Factory
